	heroEyebrow={`A Father For`}
	heroSubhead={`You pour out all day — for every student, every parent, every plan and deadline — and so often little gets poured back in. Here's the truth underneath the exhaustion: you have a Father in heaven who fills you first, so you can teach from the overflow of being loved, not the strain of being depleted.`}
